<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:28:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>当一名极端正统派定居者提出向一名极端世俗的特拉维夫人传授犹太教时，发生了什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-an-haredi-settler-offered-to-teach-an-ultra-secular-tel-avivian-about-judaism/00000190-c7d8-dfb6-afbe-effaf8a20000</link><description>有一天，有人敲我的门。那是一个极端正统的人，微笑着问我是否想学习犹太教。我邀请他进来</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 23:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-an-haredi-settler-offered-to-teach-an-ultra-secular-tel-avivian-about-judaism/00000190-c7d8-dfb6-afbe-effaf8a20000</guid></item><item><title>迈克·约翰逊威胁要逮捕扰乱内塔尼亚胡国会演讲的议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/this-is-an-attack-on-americans-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-appeal-to-republicans/00000190-c7d0-dbfd-a594-c7f76fbf0001</link><description>在共和党大会间隙的“向亲以色列民选官员致敬”上，约翰逊议长告诉共和党犹太人：我们是唯一亲以色列的政党</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 22:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/this-is-an-attack-on-americans-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-appeal-to-republicans/00000190-c7d0-dbfd-a594-c7f76fbf0001</guid></item><item><title>在 10 月 7 日之后的世界中，犹太人不再有应许之地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-post-october-7-world-there-are-no-promised-lands-for-jews/00000190-c6aa-d3e0-a5fd-efbf138a0000</link><description>去年对犹太人来说是非常不安的一年，他们感觉一段独特的宽容和安全时期可能已经结束。这不仅是哈马斯的袭击，也是以色列内部政治的事态发展</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-post-october-7-world-there-are-no-promised-lands-for-jews/00000190-c6aa-d3e0-a5fd-efbf138a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端主义政府煽动对人质的仇恨，并产生了后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-extremist-government-is-stoking-hate-against-hostages-and-there-are-consequences/00000190-c67d-de8b-adfc-df7da0bb0000</link><description>一小部分但直言不讳的以色列选民在极端主义领导人的鼓励下，猛烈抨击人质亲属在试图确保加沙被囚禁的亲人获释时所做的斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:55:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-extremist-government-is-stoking-hate-against-hostages-and-there-are-consequences/00000190-c67d-de8b-adfc-df7da0bb0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列实施武器禁运？承认巴勒斯坦吗？英国新政府即将做出的政策决定承诺“为善的力量”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/arms-embargo-on-israel-recognize-palestine-looming-policy-decisions-for-new-u-k-govt/00000190-c65a-dbfd-a594-c67fd2860000</link><description>包括外交大臣戴维·拉米在内的新英国工党政府无意卷入关于以色列和加沙的两极分化和政治有毒的政策辩论，而是更愿意在制裁暴力的约旦河西岸定居者等问题上保持共识。但正如一位专家指出的那样：“你永远无法逃避以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/arms-embargo-on-israel-recognize-palestine-looming-policy-decisions-for-new-u-k-govt/00000190-c65a-dbfd-a594-c67fd2860000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院将裁定以色列占领约旦河西岸是否非法：为什么是现在以及以色列和巴勒斯坦人将如何反应？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-why-now-and-what-will-be-the-reactions/00000190-c5ba-dbfd-a594-c5bfc8e70000</link><description>海牙最新的历史性判决：国际法院的程序与国际刑事法院有何不同？ ■ 以色列是否配合听证会？ ■ 如果法院裁定以色列对约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的占领非法，会产生什么影响？</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-why-now-and-what-will-be-the-reactions/00000190-c5ba-dbfd-a594-c5bfc8e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院强调任命最高法院院长的紧迫性，呼吁双方在8月8日之前达成妥协</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-court-stresses-urgency-of-appointing-court-president-calls-on-sides-to-compromise/00000190-c6dc-db81-a3f7-f6dc488a0000</link><description>法官们在请愿书听证会上发表讲话，该请愿书要求司法政变策划者司法部长亚里夫·莱文(Yariv Levin)任命常任法院院长。 “任命最高法院院长的必要性还有疑问吗？”奥弗·格罗斯科普夫法官表示</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:25:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-court-stresses-urgency-of-appointing-court-president-calls-on-sides-to-compromise/00000190-c6dc-db81-a3f7-f6dc488a0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 286 天：以色列议会投票反对建立巴勒斯坦国的原则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-286-knesset-voted-against-principle-of-establishing-palestinian-state/00000190-c6cc-d966-abf0-e6ec03820000</link><description>以色列议会投票反对建立巴勒斯坦国的原则 ■ 极端正统沙斯党呼吁内塔尼亚胡敲定人质协议 ■ 失去亲人的以色列家庭表示，他们正在组织建立一个民事调查委员会，在没有国家委员会的情况下 ■ 以色列在西部被弹片炸伤银行汽车爆炸 ■ 战争进入 286 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 17:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-286-knesset-voted-against-principle-of-establishing-palestinian-state/00000190-c6cc-d966-abf0-e6ec03820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级警官在被拍摄暴力逮捕反政府抗议者后被免除指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-police-officer-cleared-of-charges-after-being-filmed-violently-arresting-protester/00000190-c669-d2f8-abdb-e66dbb380000</link><description>周四早些时候，警察调查部门起诉了去年 3 月特拉维夫向反政府示威者投掷眩晕手榴弹的五名警察。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/top-police-officer-cleared-of-charges-after-being-filmed-violently-arresting-protester/00000190-c669-d2f8-abdb-e66dbb380000</guid></item><item><title>“你给我们带来的只是痛苦”：以色列议员纳马·拉齐米要求内塔尼亚胡下台的病毒式演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/you-only-brought-us-pain-viral-speech-by-israeli-mk-demanding-netanyahu-step-down/00000190-c62f-d13a-ad92-cebfac4a0000</link><description>“你是头儿，你有罪。”你们离开后，以色列将重新成为一个成功的国家，一个发展、创业和繁荣的国家，但最重要的是充满同情心、支持和希望。”阅读工党议员纳马·拉齐米 (Naama Lazimi) 的演讲全文</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:16:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/you-only-brought-us-pain-viral-speech-by-israeli-mk-demanding-netanyahu-step-down/00000190-c62f-d13a-ad92-cebfac4a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵两周前因真主党无人机袭击受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-from-hezbollah-drone-attack-two-weeks-ago/00000190-c663-db81-a3f7-f6ffe8ad0000</link><description>埃夫拉伊姆·本·阿姆拉姆 (Efraim Ben Amram) 25 岁，来自 Yesud HaMa&amp;#39;ala，在 10 个兄弟姐妹中排行第五。他的父母约瑟夫·海姆 (Yosef Haim) 和利拉赫 (Lilach) 去世了</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-from-hezbollah-drone-attack-two-weeks-ago/00000190-c663-db81-a3f7-f6ffe8ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人因违反命令而在反政府抗议活动中被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reservists-arrested-at-anti-govt-protests-suspended-in-contravention-of-orders/00000190-c61d-d2f8-abdb-e67dcd850000</link><description>陆军预备役军人（其中一些来自精锐部队）在停职前没有举行听证会，这违反了规定。一名因抗议内塔尼亚胡总理政府而被捕的士兵说，“感觉就像在战争期间，警察正在告诉军队谁可以履行预备役义务，谁不能执行预备役义务”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:25:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reservists-arrested-at-anti-govt-protests-suspended-in-contravention-of-orders/00000190-c61d-d2f8-abdb-e67dcd850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长加兰特允许军队周日向极端正统派人士发送 1,000 份征兵令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/defense-chief-gallant-okays-army-to-send-1-000-draft-orders-to-haredi-men-on-sunday/00000190-c5fc-d13a-ad92-cdff89150000</link><description>国防部长约阿夫·加兰特指示，预计发出的6000份订单将分三轮交付。著名的正统派领袖呼吁犹太学院的学生，只要没有法律确定他们的地位，就不要回应任何征兵通知</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:34:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/defense-chief-gallant-okays-army-to-send-1-000-draft-orders-to-haredi-men-on-sunday/00000190-c5fc-d13a-ad92-cdff89150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长表示，本-格维尔上任后任命的警察局长权力有限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/ag-says-ben-gvirs-chosen-police-chief-has-limited-authority-as-he-assumes-new-post/00000190-c5d5-dbfd-a594-c5f71b050000</link><description>代理警察局长阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德少将在接受腐败调查后尚未获得任命。以色列总检察长表示，在他的任命成为永久性任命之前，他无法处理任命或做出全系统决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/ag-says-ben-gvirs-chosen-police-chief-has-limited-authority-as-he-assumes-new-post/00000190-c5d5-dbfd-a594-c5f71b050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队缩短西岸检查站的工作时间，当地巴勒斯坦人取水困难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-reduces-hours-at-west-bank-checkpoint-local-palestinians-struggle-to-obtain-water/00000190-c530-d3e0-a5fd-efb514d30000</link><description>西岸北部的牧羊社区依赖邻近城镇的水箱，但通过检查站的通行时间减少到每天四个小时。一名当地巴勒斯坦人表示，“如果它关门两天，我不知道我们将如何生活”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:03:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-reduces-hours-at-west-bank-checkpoint-local-palestinians-struggle-to-obtain-water/00000190-c530-d3e0-a5fd-efb514d30000</guid></item><item><title>忘记平等：以色列的正统草案是关于枪支和黄油的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/forget-equality-the-haredi-draft-is-about-guns-and-butter/00000190-c601-d3e0-a5fd-efb5ba810000</link><description>以色列军队看到正统派士兵填补了人力短缺。财政部希望一份有利于经济的草案</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:40:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/forget-equality-the-haredi-draft-is-about-guns-and-butter/00000190-c601-d3e0-a5fd-efb5ba810000</guid></item><item><title>在圣殿山，本格维尔威胁人质交易，警告内塔尼亚胡不要达成加沙休战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/at-temple-mount-ben-gvir-threatens-hostage-deal-warns-netanyahu-not-to-reach-gaza-truce/00000190-c56e-d2f8-abdb-e56e43d60000</link><description>本-格维尔对耶路撒冷圣地的访问引起了约旦外交部和一位以色列政府部长的批评，后者谴责极右翼部长的行为是“挑衅”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:23:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/at-temple-mount-ben-gvir-threatens-hostage-deal-warns-netanyahu-not-to-reach-gaza-truce/00000190-c56e-d2f8-abdb-e56e43d60000</guid></item><item><title>民主党2024年政纲草案对以色列、加沙、反犹太主义和伊朗的看法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/what-the-draft-democratic-2024-platform-says-on-israel-gaza-antisemitism-and-iran/00000190-c182-de8b-adfc-d9a2982f0000</link><description>民主党蓝图有一整节专门讨论以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突，包括强调拜登致力于达成持久停火协议，“确保所有人质返回”。这实际上是对美以关系现状的认可，无视进步人士要求以色列承担更多责任的请求</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:02:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/what-the-draft-democratic-2024-platform-says-on-israel-gaza-antisemitism-and-iran/00000190-c182-de8b-adfc-d9a2982f0000</guid></item><item><title>五年内，以色列纳税人为内塔尼亚胡儿子的安全花费了 2150 万谢克尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/security-for-netanyahus-family-cost-israeli-taxpayers-21-5-million-shekels-in-five-years/00000190-c4c4-d3e0-a5fd-eff5f8f20000</link><description>根据信息自由请求公开的信息显示，过去五年来，以色列为内塔尼亚胡妻子和两个儿子的安全花费了 2150 万谢克尔。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:28:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/security-for-netanyahus-family-cost-israeli-taxpayers-21-5-million-shekels-in-five-years/00000190-c4c4-d3e0-a5fd-eff5f8f20000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫市中心爆炸造成数人轻伤；以色列国防军正在研究可能的无人机袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-live/mossad-chief-urges-gaza-deal-says-netanyahus-cease-fire-terms-could-nix-hostage-release/00000190-c3bc-d3a7-a79e-c3ff79830000</link><description>两名真主党高级指挥官在以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生 ■ 蓬佩奥：拜登缓解了对伊朗的压力真主党无人机袭击 ■ 内塔尼亚胡访问加沙南部拉法 ■ 三名以色列人在约旦河西岸爆炸中受轻伤 ■ 梅图拉的大楼被反坦克导弹击中 ■ 以色列国防军辛贝特行动在加沙杀死了 20 名哈马斯沙蒂营特工 ■ 美国国防部宣布关闭加沙援助码头</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:56:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-live/mossad-chief-urges-gaza-deal-says-netanyahus-cease-fire-terms-could-nix-hostage-release/00000190-c3bc-d3a7-a79e-c3ff79830000</guid></item></channel></rss>